{"tid":335664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"公廁阿叔，痾完尿洗龜頭？","createTime":"2017-07-25T17:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T06:50:50.000Z","uid":130673,"like":7,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4bd95e423de77b0e96604b0432dc8fc99762205","tid":335664,"uid":130673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T17:51:04.000Z","msg":"話說前幾日同朋友出咗旺角，細佬人有三急去左M記附近果個公廁痾尿。<br />\n咁各位巴打都知尿兜流出黎既水係用黎沖廁架啦，<br />\n當我痾痾下既時候望過隔離阿叔，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿叔一痾完就攞隻手'筆'尿兜啲水，淋落自己碌尻到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重覆'筆'咗3次，<span style=\"color: red;\">係3次阿</span><br />\n我一路痾一路呆住咁望住阿叔碌尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n企位示意：<br />\n我丨  丨阿叔丨   丨<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/014538_d7ad4a4f1be4a95849042ec0c4266659.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F014538_d7ad4a4f1be4a95849042ec0c4266659.jpg&h=dbf800f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過阿叔碌尻都幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"cb31e9f40d3d3c6906eb44ac11ca8d5b3720effd","tid":335664,"uid":71826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T17:52:36.000Z","msg":"有咩問題 你唔係架咩"},{"pid":"7dfcc313255b1e596ba33271661bcfa21b63fc21","tid":335664,"uid":130673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T17:52:56.000Z","msg":"張圖求其上網搵，唔係果到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed01634f79b964fc57766a8583663cc4b154d854","tid":335664,"uid":130673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T17:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩問題 你唔係架咩</blockquote><br />\n自細老豆冇教落，可能唔係好識規矩"},{"pid":"afad65fb38cbd3d7e57901dbea6ba93d92d0124b","tid":335664,"uid":2446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T17:57:24.000Z","msg":"下 我洗夠五次先乾淨喎<br />\n乜你成家都咁dirty㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef1f721a6a74aa73be6b819c0ab09946a24b5a7","tid":335664,"uid":88953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T17:58:57.000Z","msg":"乜唔係正確做法咩？<br />\n利申平時懶只會洗一次"},{"pid":"7f81e5795e410148fcd5aee9566dff839fb4f272","tid":335664,"uid":40318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T17:59:40.000Z","msg":"食肉菌有好嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdf45809126ba9556249cce90679ed68fe00674","tid":335664,"uid":42751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T18:00:09.000Z","msg":"日本啲神社都係咁啦"},{"pid":"357b3305cae226fd2272417d1bfda86677b810f0","tid":335664,"uid":127795,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T18:00:48.000Z","msg":"一通常一條用黎痾尿，再用另一條黎沖乾淨痾尿果條，唔會用廁所水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59666f0a4442dae00b4b5cb1e82319250e40f8e","tid":335664,"uid":127795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T18:01:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我通常一條用黎痾尿，再用另一條黎沖乾淨痾尿果條，唔會用廁所水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1e28fbe743787fdfb3d0a9f1d5f71d5a0e1c199f","tid":335664,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T18:02:09.000Z","msg":"拎上洗手盆洗"},{"pid":"77e71817ffe0d76f8ca9f08aba5e84914ee42d31","tid":335664,"uid":1585,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T18:05:28.000Z","msg